data.description: Spacious 3 bedroom 2 bath Solar home featuring  neutral tile in the common areas and wood laminate in the bedrooms. Large primary bedroom with slider to the back patio, double vanity separate shower/tub and a sizable walk in closet. The second and third bedrooms are light and bright and share the hall guest bathroom. Kitchen offers plenty of cupboard and counter space with massive a granite island & dark cabinets with access to covered patio making it great for indoor/outdoor entertaining. Enjoy the beautiful mountain views while enjoying your morning coffee from the back patio. Located just minutes away from shopping, dining, golf, polo, hockey & schools along with easy access to the world-renowned BNP tennis tournament at the Indian Wells tennis garden and the Empire Polo Club (home of the famous Coachella & Stagecoach Festivals)  This location is perfect for a primary, secondary or an investment rental (airbnb).Seller may consider a 2-1 buy down credit to buyer.
